cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR. 

This paper is about conversational machine comprehension, which involves natural language processing and understanding. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses BERT, a pre-training language model, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning). The paper also involves prediction and analysis, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
